{"tid":2514604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓外長爆粗：中國滾出南海","createTime":"2021-05-03T11:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T14:44:12.000Z","uid":125168,"like":423,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"1467b03b98aa44f2bf339ef7b005f1034cb2067e","tid":2514604,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"菲律賓外長發帖文以粗言叫中國滾出南海<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=433417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433417&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=79ef9505\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433417&h=1347be2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=433417</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】菲律賓外交部抗議中國海警和漁船在兩國有主權爭議的南海水域活動，外長洛欽更發帖文以粗言穢語叫中國離開。<br />\n<br />\n洛欽在社交網站個人帳戶發文，以粗言叫中國滾出去，又反問中國對兩國友誼做了甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓外交部同日發聲明，抗議中國海警上月尾隨、攔截在黃岩島附近巡邏和演習的菲律賓海岸防衛隊，作出危險舉動，指中方在菲律賓領海無執法權，另外又抗議中國漁船近期在菲律賓海域非法活動，中方未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓國防部長洛倫扎納昨日亦在社交網站表示，菲律賓雖然承認中國的軍力更先進，但無阻菲方捍衛國家利益，強調會繼續在西菲律賓海，即南海進行海上巡邏。"},{"pid":"60df66f87e51b99f3c1bdc8f38cb4032537515a6","tid":2514604,"uid":253016,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"繼續口頭怒屌"},{"pid":"7c0cdafeb0bd7452358bcb51d98b1e97d69395f0","tid":2514604,"uid":42820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"atna"},{"pid":"d498d07f98544d01fddc57f092159e55ceb2386f","tid":2514604,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24638c78795203249322123e88d5db48732f4b8a","tid":2514604,"uid":